room_title: Escape room "Virus X" by Escape Room Kingsport in Kingsport
review: Our work team did Virus X. It was very cool. The people were very friendly too. Highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Virus X" by Escape Room Kingsport in Kingsport
review: Our group did the room "Virus X". Had a great time and it was super fun and quite challenging at the same time! Will totally do it again!

room_title: Escape room "Virus X" by Escape Room Kingsport in Kingsport
review: We did Virus X and it was awesome! Heath was our game master and he awesome as well. We escaped in a new record time of 29:04. We will definitely be come back to do the other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Virus X" by Escape Room Kingsport in Kingsport
review: We escaped Virus X with about 15 minutes to spare! We went with 6 other friends and had an awesome time working together to solve the puzzles. Gary was great! We will definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Virus X" by Escape Room Kingsport in Kingsport
review: My family and I are on vacation from New Jersey and did the Virus room. We had so much fun. Everyone that works here is so nice! We're going back to do the Taken room before we leave.
